# Build-time secrets (Google Maps key, Google OAuth client id, …).
# `dart_defines.example.json` is the committed template; the real
# `dart_defines.json` lives only on developer machines and is
# referenced via `--dart-define-from-file=dart_defines.json`.
dart_defines.json
